items.headline: How I Met Your Mother Wiki
items.desc: How I Met Your Mother Wiki is the authoritative resource on the popular CBS sitcom How I Met Your Mother, which revolves around five 30-something characters in New York and the main character, Ted's quest to find his true love.  The wiki features character pages, episode portals, theories about "The Mother" and pages on viral promotions such as Barney's Blog.

items.title: Mother Up! Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Mother Up! Wiki
items.desc: This Wiki is for fans of the show "Mother Up!", an animated comedy showcasing the antics of Rudi Wilson, an elite music executive turned suburban housewife. Our goal is to create the most detailed archive of "Mother Up!" episodes, voice actors, and characters, as well as fan information and guides. We welcome you to the Mother Up! Wiki!
